DESCRIPTION:
This is a collection of scripts and plugins I've written for weechat. They are compatible for the 3.X API.

FILES:
rhythmbox.pl: Displays various song info in the current channel.
YaAA.pl: Yet Another Auto Away, sets you away after a configured length of idle time.

INSTALLATION:

copy the scripts into ~/.weechat/perl/autoload, and load them into Weechat using the /perl command or restart Weechat.

MISC:

See http://weechat.org/ for more information regarding how awesome Weechat is.
